TextArea_GetColour
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<TextGadgets=>textgadgets/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<textarea_get_colour>
Syntax:	TextArea_GetColour
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 0x4018 + 0xA (16418)
r3 = gadget component Id
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = foreground colour
r1 = background colour
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method gets the foreground and background colours of a text area, which are returned in R0 and R1 as 24-bit palette entries (&BBGGRR00).